SUMMARY:Head over Heels: A Night of Community & Theater Benefiting Compass Parents
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy an evening of savory bites\, sweet treats & prizes all while watching a laugh out loud musical featuring the LBGTQ+ community \n6th Street Playhouse and Compass Parents Petaluma invite you to a special fundraising evening. \nYour ticket includes savory appetizers\, decadent desserts\, exciting prizes\, and a laugh-out-loud musical celebrating queer love and LGBTQ+ community. \nAll proceeds from the evening will directly support local transgender youth and their families through Compass Parents. \nCompass Parents Petaluma is a local organization that fosters belonging\, joy\, and resilience for transgender\, nonbinary\, and gender-expansive youth and their families in Sonoma County. Compass Parents provides parent support groups\, advocacy\, education\, and free monthly family gatherings where youth build connection and community.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/head-over-heels-a-night-of-community-theater-benefiting-compass-parents/
LOCATION:6th Street Playhouse\, 52 W. 6th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Theater
GEO:38.437519;-122.724228
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=6th Street Playhouse 52 W. 6th Street Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=52 W. 6th Street:geo:-122.724228,38.437519
END:VEVENT
