SUMMARY:Revolve at Redwood Cafe
DESCRIPTION:Meet Revolve — a group of Sonoma County teens brought together by their shared love of music (and their rock-solid mentor\, Dave Silva). What started as a bunch of tweens jamming has grown into a band that’s grown up together\, evolving in sound and spirit. Over the years they’ve gone from tweens to teens\, tried out a bunch of other hobbies\, but no matter what\, they always “revolve” back to the music.
