SUMMARY:Pepper on the Run at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:A Beatles & Wings Tribute \nJoin us Friday night and experience the magic LIVE! \n  \nGet ready for a night of timeless classics as Pepper on the Run brings the music of Paul McCartney\, Wings\, and The Beatles to life on our outdoor stage. \nBlending rich harmonies\, melodic bass lines\, and that unmistakable British pop-rock sound\, this tribute captures the spirit of an era that changed music forever. Expect a set packed with favorites like “Band on the Run\,” “Maybe I’m Amazed\,” “Live and Let Die\,” and iconic Beatles hits that span from early rock ‘n’ roll to psychedelic masterpieces. \nWhether you’re a lifelong fan or just love great live music\, this is a feel-good Friday night filled with sing-alongs\, nostalgia\, and high-energy performances. \n 
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/pepper-on-the-run-at-rio-nido-roadhouse-2/
LOCATION:Rio Nido Roadhouse\, 14540 Canyon 2 Road\, Rio Nido\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
