SUMMARY:The Bring Joy Band at the Penngrove Pub
DESCRIPTION:Jason Beard’s Bring Joy \nJason Beard is a co-founding member\, guitarist and co-songwriter for Northern California’s bluegrass jam band\, Poor Man’s Whiskey. Bring Joy is a passion driven project dedicated to showcasing Northern California’s top musical talent. With a fusion of bluegrass\, Americana\, blues\, and jam\, Bring Joy puts on upbeat shows with originals and fun covers with a bluegrass twist. The atmosphere at their shows is high energy with lots of dancing and singing! \nFollow\, like\, and share Jason’s latest work on socials to stay connected to tour dates and exclusive content. Let’s keep the music alive- Bring Joy to your playlist and your next live show experience!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-bring-joy-band-at-the-penngrove-pub/
LOCATION:Penngrove Pub\, 10005 Main Street\, Penngrove\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
