SUMMARY:Forbidden Kiss LIVE - Paparazzi
DESCRIPTION:The price of fame! Paparazzi! Bring your cameras to shoot one special dance routine!\nThe Forbidden Kiss LIVE company of performers will strut their stuff before photographers\, including the audience\, who will be invited to shoot one special number!\nCheryl King emcees this exciting production\, which includes burlesque from Ultraviolette\, Bastet Dance Fitness\, and Thotty McNaughty and Kim. We welcome back Vixen\, the Forbidden Magician\, with amazing routines\, and premiere new comedy routines from Cheryl King\, Russ Andrews and Reggie K\, music from Laid Back Zach (LBZ)\, drag from Titus Androgynous\, and Underground Improv.\nAudience members will be invited to give prompts for the improv sketches\, and prizes will be awarded for best prompts. If enough people show up in costumes\, there’ll be a costume contest.\nPURCHASE IN ADVANCE AND SAVE! PLUS RESERVE A TABLE WITH OUR ZONE TICKET OPTION\nReserved seating in Zone A $27\, Zone B $22\, Zone C $17 (does not guarantee seating) Tickets at the door $27 (seating not guaranteed).\nDoors open 6:30pm. Show starts promptly at 7:30pm.\nAdult material. 18+\nOur kitchen serves our All New Menu from the time doors open until end of intermission. (Kitchen available only at events with 60 or more advance tickets sold)
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/forbidden-kiss-live-paparazzi/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Comedy,Dance Performance,Music
