SUMMARY:The Top Secret Dance Band at the Vintage Space
DESCRIPTION:From 70’s\, 80’s\, 90’s… to now\, nonstop hits\, huge energy\, and a sound designed for the dance floor. This show won’t stay secret for long!\nTop Secret Band has spent two decades ruling the Northern California private events world\, earning a reputation as the group you call when you want the dance floor packed and the night to feel electric. They are the rare band that can slip into a black-tie gala\, light up a casino showroom\, shake loose a nightclub\, or turn a backyard party into a full-blown concert. After hundreds of shows together\, their chemistry is tight and their instincts are razor sharp. They know how to read a room\, build the energy\, and keep it there. \nTheir sound is a time machine built for dancing. One moment you’re deep in a seventies groove with Earth Wind and Fire\, K.C. and the Sunshine Band\, Donna Summer\, Michael Jackson\, and the Bee Gees. The next you’re belting eighties anthems from Journey\, Pat Benatar\, Joan Jett\, A-ha\, Bon Jovi\, and Rick Springfield. Then they jump straight into nineties and two-thousands pop with Taylor Swift\, Lizzo\, Lady Gaga\, Montell Jordan\, Sir Mix-A-Lot\, Maroon 5\, Shakira\, and the full spectrum of dance floor gold. They even dip into Latin rock and salsa with the same conviction\, rolling through Santana\, Selena\, Marc Anthony\, and more. \nTop Secret is normally a six piece wrecking crew anchored by powerhouse singers and a rhythm section that doesn’t miss. When a show calls for it\, they expand with horns and additional vocalists to create a full arena-ready sound. This is a band built for celebration. Hailing from the private events circuit where the stakes are high and the expectations even higher\, they have learned how to deliver every single time. \nIf you want a night that feels big\, joyful\, and absolutely alive\, this is your band. They bring the party\, and the party does not stay secret for long.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-top-secret-dance-band-at-the-vintage-space/
LOCATION:Vintage Space at The Flamingo Resort\, 2777 Fourth St.\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.45182;-122.68916
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Vintage Space at The Flamingo Resort 2777 Fourth St. Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=2777 Fourth St.:geo:-122.68916,38.45182
END:VEVENT
