SUMMARY:March Against Stomach Cancer
DESCRIPTION:Our Annual March Against Stomach Cancer is to honor those we have lost and the more than one million people worldwide who are fighting this disease. In Memory of Sonoma Valley Resident\, John Cardinale\, is our primary west coast awareness and fundraising event to support stomach cancer research\, awareness\, and program initiatives of No Stomach For Cancer. \nAll proceeds from the $40 registration fee go to fund stomach cancer patient and caregiver programs and include an Official Event t-shirt. With your participation\, we can support stomach cancer research that needs funding now so that we can discover life-giving treatments and alternatives to stomach removal.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/march-against-stomach-cancer/
